title: Faith No More - The Interview Sessions
description:
Label: Chatback Records
Catalog#: CHATCD15
Format: CD
Country: UK
Released: 1998
Genre: Non-Music, Rock
Style: Interview
Notes:	

This one track cd is a compilation of three interviews from Australian radio.

The first is an Interview with Billy Gould from 1995.

The second Interview starting at 11.22 is an Interview and Q&A session from 1998 with Billy Gould and Mike Patton.

The third Interview from 1998 which at 25:50 with Mike Patton via satellite from Finland. The sound quality of this segment is a problematic.
